  B. conserved.
  C. multiplied.
  D. evenly distributed.

Answer with A, B, C, or D.
2026-03-13 23:11:41 | [36mINFO[0m | 期望答案：A
2026-03-13 23:11:41 | [36mINFO[0m | 提取答案：A
